{"id":313927,"type":6,"name":"霹雳封灵岛","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/de/34/313927_CnEcL.jpg","summary":"又是一个乱世，又是一场杀戮，当星落之际，当末日之秋。\r\n又是一段恩怨，又是一阙悲歌，在冷眼之际，在千年之後。\r\n七星殒落，封灵岛封印既破，十大绝代高手应然现世。争权、斗智、夺宝、寻仇。恩怨纠葛跨千年绵延而来，一场轰天辟地战役方兴未艾。魔佛波旬应时重生，它所领导的欲界第六天肆恶武林，菩提界更是首当其冲。浩劫来袭，大悲忏慧人间苦行、一代神人素还真却未知去向，一连串的谜题，随弓者箭翊手中银箭疾射而慢慢分晓展开。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>霹雳封灵岛</li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>2002年4月</li><li><span>类型: </span>霹雳布袋戏</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台湾</li><li><span>语言: </span>闽南语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>70分钟</li><li><span>台湾名称: </span>霹靂封靈島</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.pili.com.tw/</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"doing":1},"eps":[{"id":974066,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974066","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"霹靂封靈島","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974067,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974067","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"絕命七步內","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974068,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974068","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"一箭五命","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974069,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974069","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"拼先天","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974070,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974070","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"真正的妖刀","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974071,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974071","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"大屠殺","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974072,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974072","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"重登五蓮台","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974073,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974073","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"喚魔之香","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":974074,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/974074","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"再現光芒","name_cn":"